reviewText: Cute satire, ADULT HUMOR, of the original show, but, definitely ADULT VIEWING ONLY!  NOT for kids.  Funny, entertaining, and great fun! We had a lot of laughs watching this one as we were very familiar with the original series.

It's a blast from the past! Archie Bunker fans will be tickled at the antics of Ron Jeremy and the cast of this take off of "All in the Family." For novelty interest, this is a good addition to your Ron Jeremy collection (if you have one), or just to have in your stash to trot out for a few laughs with friends.
